snippet.title: Ruan Mei Trailer — "In All Does Life Flow" | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
"As one with a sensitive palate, I only need one small bite to judge the taste of a pastry."
"I favor seasonal ingredients such as fresh fruits, flowers, and herbs. Pristine slices of life preserved inside a pastry — these provide the best dopamine response food has to offer."

English Voice:
Ruan Mei — Emi Lo
